category: Gnome Mail
requires: cygwin claws-mail libgpgme11
external-source: claws-mail
sdesc: "Claws Mail PGP core plugin"
ldesc: "Places an icon in the system tray that indicates whether you 
have any new mail. A tooltip also shows the current new, unread and 
total number of messages, and a contextual menu allows the most common 
operations."
